ns1:DescriptionData.@description: From socks for lumberjacks in 1876 to today, Jockey s commitment to comfort and well-being continues with the reusable Jockey  Face Mask. Comfortable, three-ply construction includes a water-resistant outer fabric, a filter layer that blocks at least 95% of particles 0.3 microns or larger, and an inner fabric that is cooling, antimicrobial, anti-odor, moisture wicking and quick drying. This pack of three lets you wear one, wash one and always have a fresh one ready because we re in this together.

The Jockey  Forever Fit  Molded Cup Mesh Back Bra combines the shaping and support of a bra with the ease of a bralette. Molded cups enhance your natural shape beautifully while the wide infinity underband stretches, supports and keeps its shape without pinching, digging or rolling. The breathable mesh back helps you feel cooler.

ns1:DescriptionData.@description: The smooth and silky Jockey Forever Fit  Unlined Mesh Back Bra delivers the full support and coverage of a bra with the comfort of a bralette. A thin mesh lining inside the bra offers breathability, so you stay comfortable throughout your most event-packed days and nights. The blended fabric is incredibly soft, its like a second skin while unlined, wire-free cups adapt to every curve and offer flexible all-day support. Breathable mesh detailing between the cups and back adds a cooling touch. Adjustable straps help you get just the right fit.
